snippet.title: Best VGM 1846 - Tales of Graces - A Crevasse Where Winter Has Started
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 918 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1s7lAVqC0Ps

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Wii / PS3
Tales of Graces (2010)
A Crevasse Where Winter Has Started
Motoi Sakuraba
